Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(50,50)\a6)}[Gloster:发音同Gloucester]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gloster?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是应该在塞尔旺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是体形大一点的KnightMare罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早点投降不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  只用一台机体就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,18区的势力终于肃清了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于今后的行动计划
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:00:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  让你们陪我处理愚弟的身后事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说公主所在的地方就是我们的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对待11区可不能这么直截了当
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:07.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会把你逼出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛维斯的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}皇女和魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看你那个样子  好像已经在外面吃过饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,担心你是不是被卷入那个叫ZERO的人惹出的混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的电话也打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  难得C.C.来做客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一个奇特的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然只有名字的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是  哥哥的恋人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他是约定了将来的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将来是指
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是  那个  她是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  哥哥你意外地动作很快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你在干什么啊  C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弄湿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  要赶快去盥洗室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你准备换洗衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉  我会马上来收拾的  不要乱动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  刚才那是骗人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的  开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了嘛  C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是指那个  你应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你中意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我赐给你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我的行程大幅前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行程?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏布里塔尼亚的预定表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来认为开始行动还要很久才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为你能破坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只用那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算没有这个力量  我也打算做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我预料的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎是个有趣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正在被军队追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是军队  但只是其中一部分而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要稍微躲一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你打算待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男人给我睡地板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果被抓了你也会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你在一起更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果露宿的话会被送去辅导
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管你的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话我的立场就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌缠人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个没有紧张感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  你怎么得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你那时说的契约…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:40.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,福岛  高知  广岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是第七件了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自ZERO出现以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自ZERO之后  其他的团体也在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚代理执政官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那次的ORANGE事件而失去了洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他本来就不是那块料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此军队和警察的配合也变得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也给我们带来了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我们吧  藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为ZERO  布里塔尼亚变得混乱起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是我们日本解放战线重新站起来的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都传来把红莲二式交给ZERO的消息还是不确定情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.32,0:06:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太执著于ZERO的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会被人抓住把柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ORANGE到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs22}{\fad(100,100)\pos(222,195)}朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问你的问题你一概不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却反过来问我问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想回答的话不回答不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ORANGE什么的  是捏造的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那些互称同志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,却只因一个疑点就轻易分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[注：此处报刊的英文及中文翻译见附件]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界都在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界因为你而变动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是想看到这种情况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这种混乱只不过是手段之一而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界要接受更大混乱的冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第11方面军从属14107号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于杀害克洛维斯殿下的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于证据不足而被释放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  突然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:25.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我没想到下面会有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  我也没想到上面会有女孩子掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我被坏人追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  你能救救我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅殿下的就任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被那个ORANGE事件影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去  我们纯血派的忠诚会被怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚卿受了贿赂这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么ORANGE是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  杰雷米亚卿背后在做些什么是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说自己什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种和巴托雷一样的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚卿的记忆也混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿被夺走Sutherland时我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.17,0:08:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是名人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木玄武首相的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀一等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被坏人追什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵  喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤了吗喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵  喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫他等等我们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的被释放了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,证据不足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他也因为ZERO的事被好好调查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但总是我单恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会单恋的人是很善良的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才为什么撒那种谎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在意我的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?  啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得和在布里塔尼亚的时候没什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲是从本国来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到上周为止还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说到上周为止还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学生是指高中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要观光的话什么时候都可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,问题连发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我不是责怪你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  因为今天是最后的休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想要出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看11区
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里到底是怎么样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  不用找我也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我很高兴是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能再带我去一个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请吩咐  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我看看新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于上次的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就是在浴室那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能查一下对方的号码
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和那边联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个电话是学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊  果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会以这种样子回本国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不和那个女人扯上关系就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要到处乱走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧  反正是在学校内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么死板嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里可是外人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在哪里都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天也在做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她用了Geass  让她每天来这里做记号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指这个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在缔结契约的时候我是这么听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于持续时间的实验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总要理解武器的性能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你太任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个会对我有效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会做出对我们不利的事来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿贫民区已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难得人们刚刚开始回到这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对着11区果然还是不想用我的RG啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这边  对人炮弹的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那里拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗  关于ZERO的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是丘威尔卿那里来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对新宿第四空域发动非常战斗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[大公：对君主一族男子的尊称]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  大公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘威尔卿  接下来就拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是想和杰雷米亚卿联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但看样子现在不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的猪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是11区人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我们11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们输给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战败国的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些布里塔尼亚的混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你  是枢木朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉克洛维斯的枢木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  是ZERO干掉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙只不过是奴隶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己还觉得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尊严  朋友  灵魂都出卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还算是日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这条布里塔尼亚的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是受过训练的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再对同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的PrimeG和MX4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  明明还是名誉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么让他们逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们干掉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你早就杀了很多11区人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁还会认为你是好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不允许你再侮辱这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用Geass需要直接看到对方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼镜这种程度的透明度没有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有效距离大约是270米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  被施予Geass的前后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或者是中途
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会有记忆上的丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以认为是Geass介入大脑所造成的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,假设这是光学情报的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反射也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你在那么短的时间内调查了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对手是控制了世界三分之一以上的帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有所谓的谨慎过度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人姑且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是布里塔尼亚人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只用Geass来作战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对手未免也太强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要强大就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小是不对的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在只有10岁的我们看来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界非常的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饥饿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贪污  腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差别
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战争以及恐怖主义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复不断的憎恨连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的斗争游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要有谁来打断这个连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太理想了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我没有想过能让这些东西全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有傲慢到那个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能够不失去重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最起码  有一个没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像那种顺心的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要某个人胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战争就能结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果放弃了追求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲就白白牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木首相的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那场战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲不得不死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让杀害克洛维斯殿下的犯人逃掉的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在这里算算清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.81,0:17:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说发现了ZERO是假的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在科奈莉娅殿下到达上任前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要先把内部清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚  这是肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险  快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯血派的内斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你被释放了  可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又要让你陪我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:17:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是拿到Lancelot战斗资料的好机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在这里告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是Lancelot的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:18.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和四个人做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要激动  杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会把你当成战死处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会影响你家族的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玩真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  想要把我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到底为了什么而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了皇室的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的威光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同为布里塔尼亚军的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是  名誉布里塔尼亚人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向导兵器  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特别派遣想要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁  只要介入一律杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能眼睁睁地看着无意义的战斗发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[MVS：Maser Vibration Sword的缩写，镭射振动剑]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MVS?  已经被实用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是到这个地步也不能退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴之间为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来救我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么至少也要干掉ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杰雷米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[维蕾塔·纽 Villetta Nu,纯血派战士]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,维蕾塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还想继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于能理解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要使用CHAOS炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,单手就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三方  都请收起手中的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以我之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难  难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亚第三公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Euphemia Li Britannia]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:42.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这里的指挥权交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是…公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.84,0:20:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不常在公众面前出现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实…实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是刚才太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如同你失去了父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也失去了兄长克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能否为了创造不再失去重要的人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而助我一臂之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  深感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了  由菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种场合请叫我总督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我们是亲姐妹所以更要遵守这些规定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你那边的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我们已经准备了盛大的宴会欢迎皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:22:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,松懈了  愚蠢了  堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住帝国居民的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,转入这所阿修佛德学园的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对莎莉和利瓦尔他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连对朱雀和娜娜莉也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.66,0:23:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果C.C.说她是我的共犯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也只有做了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想对自己撒谎了
